817
00:59:14,730 --> 00:59:16,920
Sangat memalukan.

818
00:59:18,330 --> 00:59:19,360
Ada apa?

819
00:59:19,360 --> 00:59:22,580
Ini sangat memalukan.

820
00:59:22,580 --> 00:59:25,890
