864
01:02:51,800 --> 01:03:01,700
♫ Aku hancur dan berhamburan setiap hari ♫

865
01:03:01,700 --> 01:03:09,210
♫ Kisah cinta kecil, festivalku sendiri ♫

866
01:03:12,550 --> 01:03:15,180
♫ Ya ampun, ♫

867
01:03:15,200 --> 01:03:22,500
